OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy this morning,
OL,6,Fscattered showers or thundery
OL,7,Fdownpours bring the potential for
OL,8,Ffrequent lightning, although not
OL,9,Feverywhere will see these. Drier and
OL,10,Fsunnier this afternoon, becoming
OL,11,Fwidely very warm or hot inland, away
OL,12,Ffrom the cooler, breezier Lincolnshire
OL,13,Fcoastline.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTonight:FChance of an isolated shower
OL,16,For thunderstorm during the evening,
OL,17,Fotherwise a fine and dry night. Rather
OL,18,Fwarm for many eastern areas, although
OL,19,Ffeeling slightly fresher in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
