OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA dry, mostly sunny day,
OL,6,Fperhaps the chance for some rain or
OL,7,Fshowers in the south for a time.
OL,8,FFeeling fresher inland, but warmer at
OL,9,Fthe coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry,
OL,12,Flargely sunny and warm or very warm on
OL,13,FSaturday. Trending cooler and more
OL,14,Fchangeable from Sunday. An increased
OL,15,Fchance of rain, but still some fine,
OL,16,Fwarm weather at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
